author: @supremeoverlorde2109
comment:
What we got was really well-made and action-packed, so I'm not THAT disappointed, but I do think it's a bit of a shame that we've been getting fewer and fewer cutscenes in the main story. Under Deepspace and Long-Awaited Revelry were packed with them. Homecoming Wings is where I really started noticing the comparative lack of cutscene material and I think this was the first main story update that included full chapters without a single cutscene. 

Like I get that the main story isn't directly what's bringing in the big bucks, but it IS a big part of what keeps a lot of players sticking around and I feel like it wouldn't have been too much to ask for at least one animated scene per chapter. Even if the others weren't as action-heavy. Honestly, one of the biggest things for me is that I just want more opportunities to hear MC's voice. She was fantastic in the Sylus scene and then hardly had any dialogue in the Zayne one.
title: Love and Deepspace | Death and Rebirth
